videos.headline: Oregon starts off second quarter with a steal and a bucket
videos.description: Oregon guard Ahlise Hurst comes up with a steal and breaks away for the easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Oregon starts off second quarter with a steal and a bucket) 2023/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Charlisse Leger-Walker sinks smooth jumper for Washington State
videos.description: Washington State guard Charlisse Leger-Walker drops in a jumper from the corner to extend the Cougars' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Charlisse Leger-Walker sinks smooth jumper for Washington State) 2023/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oregon draws late foul, ties game at the line to force OT
videos.description: Oregon's Grace VanSlooten draws a foul with less than a second to go and knocks down her free throws to force overtime vs. Washington State.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Oregon draws late foul, ties game at the line to force OT) 2023/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oregon misses game-winning shot as Washington State holds on in OT
videos.description: Oregon's Te-Hina Paopao misses a potential game-winning jumper in overtime as Washington State holds on for a 85-84 win.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Oregon misses game-winning shot as Washington State holds on in OT) 2023/01/15 ESHEET
